entry.title: When God's Will doesn't go your way

media:group.media:title: When God's Will doesn't go your way
media:group.media:description:
Source: https://www.podbean.com/eau/pb-trzy2-190c27c
Ever prayed for God’s guidance, followed His lead, and still faced crushing defeat? Sounds like a nightmare, right? In this episode, we dive into a shocking story where God’s people spiral into chaos, civil war erupts, and even His chosen ones lose battles they were told to fight. Why does God’s plan sometimes feel like a failure? Join us for a lighthearted yet deep dive into patience, persistence, and trusting God when His path takes a wild turn. Learn why instant success isn’t always the goal and how to keep seeking God when things go wrong. Catch it on all major platforms or watch the video on The Lion Company’s YouTube channel. Visit thelioncompany.org for more!
#Podcast #FYP #Reels #Faith #GodsPlan #ChristianLife #TrustGod #SpiritualGrowth #TheLionCompany #FaithJourney #Viral #Inspiration

entry.title: Confessions of a Truth Teller: The Dark side of Being Light

media:group.media:title: Confessions of a Truth Teller: The Dark side of Being Light
media:group.media:description:
Source: https://www.podbean.com/eau/pb-tn6vp-18b2e5d
In this episode of The Lion Company Podcast, we dive into the power and peril of truth. Why is honesty so hard? How can it hurt yet heal? Join us as we explore the courage it takes to speak truth in love, from marriage to ministry, and uncover wisdom for navigating life’s most difficult conversations.

Miracle or Madness?
media:group.media:description: In this deeply personal conversation, Jonathan and Gina sit down to explore radical forgiveness, supernatural encounters, and the breathtaking possibilities of genuine faith. From miraculous “gold teeth” and growing taller—twice!—to overcoming painful pasts and suicidal thoughts, they share raw testimonies of how an authentic relationship with God can transform every aspect of life. If you’ve ever questioned the bounds of the impossible, this episode will challenge and inspire you to believe for more. Watch or listen to the full-length episode on our website at www.thelioncompany.org, YouTube, or wherever you get your podcasts. Don't forget to like, sub and comment! #Episode5 #TheLionCompany #Forgiveness #Faith #Miracles #Supernatural #Testimony #Deliverance #SpiritualGrowth #GoldTeeth #GrowingTaller #Podcast #ChristianPodcast #Inspiration #RadicalFaith
